{% call components.section("Best practices") -%}

  <p>Use existing spacers for horizontal and vertical spacing. If a current spacer doesn’t meet your needs, <a href="../../get-started/">submit a request</a> for us to establish new spacers.</p>

  <div class="margin-bottom--4">
   <img src="{{ '/assets/spacing/spacing-best-practice-1.svg' | url }}" alt="Use existing spacers" style="">
  </div>

